'''Diomazul''' is a minor [[Vudra|Vudran]] war [[god]] represented as a [[snake|serpent]] with many arms each holding a blade. He is known to be brutal in battle.<ref>{{Cite book/Escape from Old Korvosa|54}}</ref>

